programme.title: Robot Wars
programme.desc: One competitor draws first blood only seconds into the first round. After suffering severe damage at the hands of another competitor, one robots chance at the finals may be lost.

programme.title: Robot Wars
programme.desc: The last chance for combatants to fight for a place in the Grand Final. With the newcomers outnumbering the veterans, will the first timers make up for their lack of experience?

programme.title: Robot Wars
programme.desc: This episode, a new Robot Wars champion will emerge! Sparks and scraps are sure to fly in this explosive series finale. Winners will have to make it through the four-way melees and head-to-head battles to be able to prove themselves in the final.

programme.title: Robot Wars
programme.desc: Newcomers, veterans and a recent President enter the fray in this first Heat of the series. Competitors are eliminated left, right and centre and only the strongest will survive to compete in the finals.

programme.title: Robot Wars
programme.desc: A veteran only heat features the current reigning Champions, Carbide. Will Carbide’s streak be brought to an end by the other robots, more experienced and eager than ever?

programme.title: Robot Wars
programme.desc: Even the judges aren’t safe as two robots collide, sending shrapnel through the bullet-resistant shields around the arena. Two very different styles of robot meet in the finals.

programme.title: Robot Wars
programme.desc: One newcomer stares down seven veterans, will their induction into the arena be successful, or will their inexperience find them in the pit? One robot will have a second chance to qualify in the Redemption Round.

programme.title: Robot Wars
programme.desc: The final heat features only veterans, here for an opportunity to make up for their mistakes in the previous tournaments. Only one competitor will make it into the Grand Finals, and the others must suffer defeat, again.

programme.title: Robot Wars
programme.desc: After lengthy repairs and inspirational pep talks, the qualifiers prepare to fight for the title. A 10-way Robot Rumble will give the victor a spot in the Grand Finals, alongside the heat winners.

programme.title: MechMania
programme.desc: Robot fightings newest competition begins! In the first heat, meet new robots and some familiar faces as teams get a feel for the arena and size up their competition. Filmed in Grantham in front of a live audience, robots battle for survival in the Robots Live Arena.

programme.title: MechMania
programme.desc: Heat 2 of the UKs most brutal robot combat competition takes the action to Crawley in the south of England. Winners and losers from Heat 1 face fresh opponents, fighting to secure a win and guarantee their place in the finals.

programme.title: MechMania
programme.desc: Its the last chance for teams to secure a spot before the final. In savage and tactical 1v1 matches, teams battle for a place in the top 16. New robots join the fray, hoping for a last-minute victory to advance to the championship.

programme.title: MechMania
programme.desc: The most battle-hardened combat robots in the UK compete in the MechMania Grand Final. After three grueling heats, only the toughest survive. The tournament is now a single-elimination, 1v1, sudden-death formatuntil one team emerges as the victorious champion.

programme.title: Robot Wars
programme.sub-title: S04 : E01 Ultimate Collection: House Robots
programme.desc: An extensive and informative dive behind-the-scenes on the House Robots. Get inside information from designer Chris Reynolds, on what goes into creating these killing machines.

programme.title: Robot Wars
programme.desc: Follow Team Chaoss journey. From humble beginnings to how they ended up building one of the most feared Robots ever to compete.

programme.title: The Greatest
programme.desc: Allen och Grace Brewer har forlorat sin aldsta son i en bilolycka, nar det plotsligt ringerpå dorren. Utanfor står Rose. Hon sager att hon kande deras son. Och att hon vantar hans barn. Forst får det familjen att falla isar ytterligare. Men kanske kan avenden svåraste olycka leda till ny lycka?

programme.title: The Dreamers
programme.desc: Tre cineaster – den amerikanske utbytesstudenten Matthew och tvillingparet Theo och Isabelle – har kommit varandra nara genom sitt gemensamma intresse. Matthew fascineras av Theo och Isabelles oortodoxt intima band. Nar tvillingarnas foraldrar reser bort en månad bjuds Matthew in att bo hos dem, och de forlorar sig i filmisk fantasi. The Dreamers ar ett romantiskt drama av Oscarsbelonade Bernardo Bertolucci, med Michael Pitt, Louis Garrel och Eva Green i huvudrollerna.

programme.title: Programmet fortsatter strax
programme.desc: Vi tar igen vår skonhetssomn! Stanna kvar for mer prisvard underhållning utvald av Rakuten TV.

programme.title: Griffin and Phoenix
programme.desc: Nar Griffin har fått diagnosen att han har dodlig cancer bestammer han sig for att ta livet i egna hander och ha lite kul innan han dor. Samtidigt som tiden for hans liv rinner ut traffar han och blir kar i Phoenix - som också har en hemlighet.

programme.title: Wingman, Inc
programme.desc: Bobby Tomkins jobbar som en professionell djurpsykolog och overtalats av sina vanner att praktisera sina fantastiska fardigheter som deras wingman bland tjejer. Och nar han antligen hittar sin egen efterlangtade karlek har han ingen aning om att Kristy ar hans absolut varsta tankbara rival. En ”man blocker” i varldsklass. Men i karlekens universum finns det inga spelregler, och enbart en av dem kan stå på tronen som nummer 1.

programme.title: Equals
programme.desc: I en utopisk varld, dar våld och brott i princip ar utplånade via genetisk eliminering av kanslor, lever personer som Nia och Silas ett lugnt, handelselost och dronarlikt liv. De arbetar med att producera informationsmaterial på ett stort kontor och utvaxlar enbart artighetsfraser. Livet ar enkelt, anda till dess att ett rykte borjar florera: en sjukdom som orsakar att manniskor visar kanslor har brutit ut. Om det upptacks av overheten skickas de infekterade ivag, for att aldrig återvanda. Silas misstanker att han bar på sjukdomen och nar det bekraftas, blir han en paria. Trots det dras han till Nia, som också ar infekterad men har lyckats dolja symptomen battre an han sjalv.

programme.title: Stay Cool
programme.desc: Forfattaren Henry återvander till sin hemstad for att arbeta som larare. Han måste konfrontera sina kanslor for sin gamla karlek Scarlet, samt bemota studenten Shastas spirande karlek till honom.

programme.title: Bottled with Love
programme.desc: Abbey ar mitt i karriaren, olycklig, frustrerad och hopplost uppgiven efter alla misslyckade dater. Hennes mormor foreslår att hon skriver ner alla hennes onskningar som ett karleksbrev rakt från hjartat. Motvilligt foljer hon rådet och stoppar ner brevet i en flaska och slanger ut den i hamnen. Tiden går och månader senare hamnar Abbey i ett projekt med hennes chefs son Nick. Han ska aven av en handelse hittat flaskan med Abbeys brev, helt ovetande om att det ar hon som skrivit. Sakta borjar Nick forstå kopplingen och får det valdigt jobbigt med situationen och hemligheten. Han beslutar att beratta om det funna brevet. Abbey ber honom dra åt helvete som fort henne bakom ljuset.

programme.title: Wicker Park
programme.desc: Matthew och Lisa ar oskiljaktiga. Deras passionerade karlek går inte att ta miste på. Men så plotsligt forsvinner hon- lamnar honom utan ett ord- och Matthews varld rasar samman. Nu, två år senare, har Matthew borjat komma over den varsta saknaden. Men nar han plotsligt får vad han tror ar en skymt av henne i folkvimlet ar det som att han blivit traffad av blixten- han måste få se henne. Efter ett intensivt letande hittar han henne. Tror han. For nar smartan och begaret blir for stort kan den forvranga dina sinnesbilder.

programme.title: Modern Persuasion
programme.desc: En modern version av Jane Austens roman ”Övertalning”. Wren Cosgrove ar en lycklig och framgångsrik karriarkvinna som varje kvall kommer hem till sin katt. Nar hennes firma anlitas av Owen Jasper, han som var den ratte, så vacks gamla kanslor till liv och Wren får en ny chans att uppleva den sanna karleken.

programme.title: You and Me
programme.desc: En ung, dov kvinna moter en man som nyligen har blivit blind. Vad som foljer ar en rolig och rorande karlekshistoria om livets stora utmaningar och lyckliga stunder

programme.title: Bad Cupid
programme.desc: Archie ar en gud på uppdrag att sakerstalla så karleken alltid vinner oavsett vad. Eller åtminstone någorlunda så nar som på att man kanske dor på kuppen for den som forsoker. Egentligen så ar han inte så noga med vad resultatet blir. Hans installning som Amors forlangda arm till romantik och karlek ar snarare ratt så halvhjartad, som man bor se upp for om man hamnar i hans vag nar ska forsoker komma med en hjalpande hand. Speciellt dom som han verkligen forsoker hjalpa.

programme.title: Some Girl(s)
programme.desc: En kort tid innan han ska gifta sig reser en framgångsrik forfattare (Adam Brody) landet runt for att besoka fem gamla flickvanner (Jennifer Morrison, Mía Maestro, Emily Watson, Zoe Kazan och Kristen Bell) i ett forsok att gottgora gamla synder och oforratter.

programme.title: Dubbelt begar
programme.desc: Dubbelt begar berattar historien om den unga kvinnan Chloe, som benagen till depression påborjar terapi och dar blir foralskad i sin psykoterapeut Paul. Efter ett par månader flyttar hon in hos sin nya alskare men upptacker snabbt att han doljer en del av sin identitet for henne.

programme.title: Don Jon
programme.desc: Don Martell ar en kille från New Jersey, vars liv kretsar kring familjen, vannerna, kyrkan – och porr. Formågan att ragga upp nya tjejer varje helg har gett honom smeknamnet ”Don Jon”. En kvall traffar han den snygga och romantiska Barbara som letar efter en underbar dromkille, en idealbild som ar valdigt långt från Don.

programme.title: Unleashed
programme.desc: Emma (Kate Micucci) har aldrig haft turen att finna karleken. Hon trivs battre med att spendera tid tillsammans med sin katt och sin hund. Av ett underligt kosmiskt ode forvandlas hennes husdjur till den basta manskliga versionen av dem sjalva. Katten blir en stilig, mystisk Diego (Justin Chatwin) och hennes hund blir en lekfull och alskvard Sam (Steve Howey). De tavlar om hennes uppmarksamhet, medan Emma inte har en aning om att hennes husdjur har forvandlats till manniskor. Detta leder till dråpliga dejter och komiska, udda situationer. Sakta men sakert borjar Emma omvardera sina tankar om att dejta och borjar i stallet fundera over mojligheten att faktiskt kunna alska.

programme.title: Programmet fortsatter strax
programme.desc: Vi tar igen vår skonhetssomn! Stanna kvar for mer prisvard underhållning utvald av Rakuten TV.

programme.title: Whats Your Number?
programme.desc: Ally Darling inleder en stravan efter att finna den basta "ex" av hennes liv, på något satt som behovs, nar hon laser en tidningsartikel som varnar for att manniskor som har haft 20 eller fler relationer har saknat sin chans till sann karlek. Allys hunky nya granne Colin (Chris Evans) hjalper henne att spåra hennes exes, i utbyte mot Ally som hjalper Colin att undvika hans.

programme.title: Burning Man
programme.desc: Tom ar chefskock på en chic restaurant på Bondi beach i Sydney. Han ar en arrogant typ som ser flyktigt på tillvaron. Han beter sig sjalviskt och allmant illa mot sina kollegor och sin 8-årige son Oscar, men aven mot de många kvinnorna i hans liv, exfrun Karen, kollegan Sally, psykologen Miriam, Lisa som ar lyckligt gift, prostituerade Lesley och maklaren Carol som skulle salja hans hus. Men Tom har inte alltid varit osympatisk. For tio år sedan traffade han vackra, perfekta Sarah. Hon tog fram det basta hos Tom och gav honom deras gemensamma son.

programme.title: Couples Vacation
programme.desc: Jack Spencer ar en tidigare hyllad bastsaljande forfattare som inte får till en ny bastsaljare. Forfattarkarriaren och hans aktenskap ar i kris och darfor åker han och hans fru Amanda till en glampingretreat långt från civilisationen i jakt på den gnista som skulle kunna få deras karlek att borja gloda igen. En smått chockartad dubbelbokning gor deras romantiska vistelse på tu man hand till allt annat an vad de hade tankt sig och nar en snygg och bekymmerslos framling forsoker forfora Amanda så befinner Jack sig plotsligt mitt i ett humoristiskt utforskande av karlek, svartsjuka, grusade drommar och sunt småstadsfornuft.

programme.title: We Too Together
programme.desc: Rob kampar med PTSD efter att ha kommit hem ifrån kriget. Långsamt lar han sig att overvinna sitt forflutna. Under julhelgerna moter han Gabriela som han fullstandigt faller for, och hon alskar honom precis som han ar. Vandning ar total och livet får åter en mening.

programme.title: My Super Ex
programme.desc: Denna sanslosa komedi bevisar att det kan vara rent av livsfarligt att gora slut. Matt (Luke Wilson) tror sig ha funnit den ratta nar han traffar Jenny (Uma Thurman) som ar både sexig och smart... Men nar Matt bestammer sig for att gora slut, blir det något han snart kommer att ångra...

programme.title: I Love You Phillip Morris
programme.desc: Steve Russell (Jim Carrey) ar lyckligt gift med Debbie (Leslie Mann) och en monsterinvånare i staden dar de bor. En bilolycka får honom att drastiskt omvardera sitt liv. Steven inser genom en uppenbarelse att han ar gay och beslutar sig for att leva sitt liv fullt ut, aven om det innefattar att bryta mot lagen. Stevens nya syn på livet gor att han ganska snabbt hamnar i fangelset. Dar tar livet annu en ny vandning och han blir galet kar i Phillip Morris, en kanslosam och lågmald kille (Ewan McGregor). Stevens hangivelse att få leva ett liv i frihet tillsammans med Phillip driver Steve till fler och flera innovativa brott.

programme.title: Shes The Man
programme.desc: Nar Violas bror drar till London passar hon på att hanga på hans internatskola. Utkladd till sin bror blir Viola kar i en av fotbollsspelarna i skollaget men inser snart att det ar betydligt fl er an hon (han) som har karleksproblem… Duke vill ha Olivia som gillar Sebastian som egentligen ar Viola. Violas brorsa traffar Monique så hon hatar Olivia som hanger med Duke for att gora Sebastian svartsjuk. Sebastian ar ju egentligen Viola som ar kar i Duke som tror att hon ar en snubbe... Hangde ni med?

programme.title: Youth In Revolt
programme.desc: Michael Cera spelar rollen som Nick Twisp. En unik och alskvard tonåring med smak for livets sofistikerade gladjeamnen, såsom Sinatra och Fellini. På en campingsemester med familjen foralskar han sig i den vackra, intelligenta och frigjorda Sheeni Saunders (Portia Doubleday). Men geografi, familj och svartsjuka ex-partners konspirerar for att hålla Nick och Sheeni åtskilda. Efter uppmuntran från Sheeni overger Nick sitt tråkiga, forutsagbara liv och utvecklar ett rebelliskt alter ego: Francois Dillinger. Med mustasch, slips, djup rost och bad boy-attityd kan inget stoppa Francois från att vara tillsammans med Sheeni.

programme.title: All For Her
programme.desc: Devina och hennes man Rick langtar efter barn. Efter år av missfall blir Devina antligen gravid. Men det visar sig att hon lider av en dodlig sjukdom. Nu borjar en kamp mot klockan, Devina måste overleva tills barnet ar fott…

programme.title: The Greatest
programme.desc: Allen och Grace Brewer har forlorat sin aldsta son i en bilolycka, nar det plotsligt ringerpå dorren. Utanfor står Rose. Hon sager att hon kande deras son. Och att hon vantar hans barn. Forst får det familjen att falla isar ytterligare. Men kanske kan avenden svåraste olycka leda till ny lycka?

programme.title: No Stranger Than Love
programme.desc: Vad kan vara konstigare an att ett stort hål oppnar sig i Lucy Sherringtons vardagsrumsgolv? Jo, karleken, som det visar sig.Det finns inte en man i stan som inte ar kar i Lucy. Hon ar snall, sympatisk, rolig och lojal – hon ar den perfekta tjejen som inte kan gora något fel. Ändå har hon gått med på en traff med Clint som ar gift och coach for footballaget. Precis nar de ska påborja sin affar trillar Clint ner i ett hål som oppnar sig i Lucys vardagsrum. Men det ar inte vilket hål som helst; det ar det eviga morkrets interdimensionella och enkelriktade hål. Clint fastnar nere i hålet och svavar runt i ett oandlighetens mellantillstånd.

programme.title: Hard Luck Love Song
programme.desc: Ett romantiskt drama kantat av countrymusik. Den charmerande men otursforfoljde Jesse driver runt utan riktning i livet. Nar en gammal flamma dyker upp inser Jesse att han står vid ett vagskal i livet och att han måste valja mellan att fortsatta fatta dåliga beslut eller att ta sig i kragen.

programme.title: Love and Honor
programme.desc: Nar en ung soldat i Vietnam blir dumpad av sin hemstadstjej, bestammer han och hans basta van att gå AWOL och återvanda till staterna for att vinna tillbaka henne.

programme.desc: In this stage in Curacao no one wants to lose the chance to fight for one kilo gold in World grand finals in Dubai.

programme.desc: The last chance to qualify for the World Grand Finale. Zageris and Belsak fight for the better position for the finals.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League

programme.desc: We reach Dubai where we will crown the new champion for SCL 2016. This is part one of the world finals.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S03 : E16 SCL 2016 Season 3, Episode 16, Dubai World grand finals (Part 2)
programme.desc: In this last episode, the best athletes compete in Pole Push, Deadlift, Forward Hold and Loading.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S04 : E01 SCL 2017 Season 4, Episode 1, Norway
programme.desc: We are in beautiful Norway for the kick off of the 2017 MLO Strongman Champions League season. With partly cloudy weather and lots of snow, we have the perfect scenery for the athletes, who prepare for the first contest of the year.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S04 : E02 SCL 2017 Season 4, Episode 2, Germany
programme.desc: A definite highlight in this FIBO edition in Germany, Strongman Champions League introduced its new rules for a special team item. Graham Hicks tries here to set a New World Record on the biggest log in the world, currently held by Krzysztof Radzikowski. Boosted also by the presence of the acclaimed in the strongman circles names of Mark Felix and Danis Zageris.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S04 : E03 SCL 2017 Season 4, Episode 3, Lithuania
programme.desc: This weekend sees the Strongman Champions League Log Lift World Championships in Lithuania. Big lifting names such as Graham Hicks , Vidas Blekaitis and Vytatus Lalas are in the startlist to push some big numbers.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S04 : E04 SCL 2017 Season 4, Episode 4, Holland
programme.desc: The battle of the Dutch will take place this edition in Lichtenvoorde, a place very well known in Holland because of the famous “Black Cross”. The athletes will compete over six heavy events and the winner gets 25 Strongman Champions League ranking points.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S04 : E05 SCL 2017 Season 4, Episode 5, Serbia
programme.desc: Set in the beautiful mountain resort Zlatibor, the fifth stage of the Strongman Champions League 2017 sees 14 athletes from across the world competing for the gold medal of SCL Serbia 2017. The event welcomes top-athlete - and odds-on favourite - Matjaz Belsak (Slovenia), who has presented himself in an impressive shape so far. Can his opponents defeat him?

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S04 : E06 SCL 2017 Season 4, Episode 6, Canada (Part 1)
programme.desc: The next two stages take place in Quebec. With eight events over two days, SCL Canada is a true ‘heavyweight’. The athletes compete in: Truck Pull, Deadlift with cars, Log Lift, and the Atlas Stones. The World’s Strongest Viking Jean-Francois Caron from Canada is a favourite, as well as current SCL leader Matjaz Belsak (Slovenia) and promising underdog Jimmy Paquet (Canada).

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S04 : E07 SCL 2017 Season 4, Episode 7, Canada (Part 2)
programme.desc: Welcome to the second day in Quebec. The athletes are fighting hard to win this two-day event. The last points of this SCL stage can be won over four outstanding disciplines: Power Stairs, Dumbbell Press, Keg Toss, and finally, the legendary Farmer’s Walk. Who will leave Canada with the yellow ‘Leader Shirt’?

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S04 : E08 SCL 2017 Season 4, Episode 8, Finland (Part 1)
programme.desc: Stages 8 and 9 of the SCL are hosted in Vaasa, Finland, taking place over a spectacular two-day event. After 3 wins so far, Matjaz Belsak from Slovenia plans to extend his lead at the top of the table. Among the other 13 highly motivated strongmen, two SCL legends will make their comeback to the competition: Former World Champion of 2015, Krzysztof Radzikowski (Poland) and Dainis Zageris (Latvia).

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S04 : E09 SCL 2017 Season 4, Episode 9, Finland (Part 2)
programme.desc: The fight for the Finnish trophy continues. In this unmissable SCL event, the strongmen battle for the win in the Carry and Drag, the Forward Hold, Deadlifting with Cars and the Loading Race. Belsak, Radzikowski and Zageris look good after the first day, but the others haven’t given up yet.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S04 : E10 SCL 2017 Season 4, Episode 10, Finland Lightweight World Championship
programme.desc: This under 105kg category event is the ultimate preparation for up-and-coming strongman athletes before entering the heavy class. The Lightweight World Championship is a special every year in the SCL calendar as it sees new talents rise and many promising athletes who are gearing up for future tournaments. A total of 25 athletes from 16 different countries make their way to Kokkola, Finland

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S04 : E11 SCL 2017 Season 4, Episode 11, Romania
programme.desc: Situated in the very heart of the Carpathian Mountains, Sibiu is a Romanian town where the climate is pleasantly mild, offering some of the best weather conditions for a strongman event around Europe. All this, without doubt, set the mood for the high results and showtime vibes in Stage 11 of Strongman Champions League. The competition in Sibiu was organized in six different disciplines

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S04 : E12 SCL 2017 Season 4, Episode 12, Curacao
programme.desc: From now on every stage of these series will be more than crucial. Curacao is a beautiful Dutch island in the Caribbean, with a great atmosphere to hold another stage of the MLO Strongman Champions League. Let’s see who takes the title here and who will secure a place in the next stage.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S04 : E13 SCL 2017 Season 4, Episode 13, Jordan
programme.desc: Ten of the world’s strongest men gathered in Amman to compete in Jordan’s first-ever Truck-Pull Championship. The contestants race against the clock while pulling a 21-ton truck across the track. One of the most fierce competitors to take part in the event was four-time winner of the World’s Strongest Man competition, Brian Shaw.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S04 : E14 SCL 2017 Season 4, Episode 14, Greece
programme.desc: Taking place in Corinth, Greece, considered by many the cradle of the sports competition games, an epic strongman battle will mark the last stage before the upcoming big two-day season’s finale in Chetumal, Mexico. In front of more than 5000 spectators, the twelve athletes compete in Log Lifts, Card Deadlift, Conan’s Wheel and Loading.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S04 : E15 SCL 2017 Season 4, Episode 15, Mexico World Finals (Part 1)
programme.desc: The first day of the two-part finale sees the strongest men competing in Carry and Drag, Dumbbell Lift and the Truck Pull. Everything is possible in this heated fight for the crown against the backdrop of stunning Chetumal, Mexico.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S04 : E16 SCL 2017 Season 4, Episode 16, Mexico World Finals (Part 2)
programme.desc: On the second day of the grand finale of the 2017 Strongman Champions League, the athletes have a last chance to secure the medals in the spectacular four events Weight for Height, Deadlift Cars, Forward Hold and The Loading Medley. Be prepared for stunning performances – and even world records!

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S05 : E01 SCL 2018 Season 5, Episode 1, Norway - World Strongest Viking
programme.desc: Season 2018 begins with 14 strongest men in the world, all competing for the title. The competition kicks off in Norway. We’ll see typical Viking disciplines, team events and world records in heavy conditions in the land of snow and ice. They will suffer, they will freeze and fight in this first competition of the year for the title that they will carry on their shoulders throughout whole year.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S05 : E02 SCL 2018 Season 5, Episode 2, Germany - FIBO Power
programme.desc: The next stop in strongest league of the world is muscle capital, largest number of strong shoulders per capichampions league on the planet. It’s a FIBO - the biggest expo on planet Earth and the second stage of 2018 Strongman champions league, in Cologne, Germany.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S05 : E03 SCL 2018 Season 5, Episode 3, Abu Dhabi
programme.desc: For the first time in history, Strongman Champions League will set up competition in Abu Dhabi. The line-up of super athletes, who are part of the SCL, includes former world champions Dainis Zageris (Latvia) and Krzysztof Radzikowski (Poland), current world champion Matjaz Belsak (Slovenia) and biggest strongman in the World Sean O’Hagan (Ireland).

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S05 : E04 SCL 2018 Season 5, Episode 4, Holland (Part 1)
programme.desc: Strongman classic in land where there is no place for anything else excepts strength, fight and endurance. Here are fourteen of the strongest men, fighting for the title of strongest in Holland.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S05 : E05 SCL 2018 Season 5, Episode 5, Holland (Part 2)
programme.desc: We go back to Holland, where former champion Dainis Zageris is in leading position after the first three events. Alongside Radzikowski, he is in this moment favorite for world title, and also leader shirt holder.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S05 : E06 SCL 2018 Season 5, Episode 6, Finland
programme.desc: Stage six of Strongman champions league, 2018 is set back on north, in Finland. Here we have Matjaz Belsak, wearing SCL leader shirt, one of the biggest strongman in the World Mika Torro, fan favorite strongman in all over the World – Will Baggott, and also big name from Baltic – Aivars Smaukstelis

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S05 : E07 SCL 2018 Season 5, Episode 7, Serbia
programme.desc: Twelve strongman, including defending Worldchampion Matjaz Belsak from Slovenia , will compete on “Air spa” for the title of best in homeland country of Tesla, Pupin, Novak Djokovic. Matjaz Belsak is the SCL leader in this competition, chasing his third victory this season.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S05 : E08 SCL 2018 Season 5, Episode 8, Finland - U105 (Part 1)
programme.desc: The World championship in lightweights of the Strongman Champions League bring to us 50 strongmen from all over the world. All athletes are under 105 kilograms and for them this is the step up to the ultimate heavyweights.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S05 : E09 SCL 2018 Season 5, Episode 9, Finland - U105 (Part 2)
programme.desc: In this second stage of the World championship of lightweights we will find out who out of the 12 athletes will win the title in the under 105 kilogram category.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S05 : E10 SCL 2018 Season 5, Episode 10, Romania (Part 1)
programme.desc: The first part of SCL Romania 2018 will be hosted in Brasov. This episode features a new event for Strongman Champion League: “ The Chopper Pull”!

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S05 : E11 SCL 2018 Season 5, Episode 11, Romania (Part 2)
programme.desc: After three classical Strongman events – Dead lift, Loading and Front hold – and one historical, Chopper Pull for the first time in history of Strongman, now we go to find out who will take title in Romania. This is the second stage in Romania and it remains to be seen who will win the title; Aivars, Travis or Krzyzstof?

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S05 : E12 SCL 2018 Season 5, Episode 12, Curacao (Part 1)
programme.desc: The next destination of Strongman Champions League is in a piece of paradise on earth – Curacao. We bring to you some special Strongman events like the Rock Lift, Tug of War and Weight for Height in this episode.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S05 : E13 SCL 2018 Season 5, Episode 13, Curacao (Part 2)
programme.desc: This is the last competition before the grand finals. After the first three events Zageris is in top place, but can O’Hagan, Baggott, Petursson and Ortmayer step into the final? Last chance some of them will find through events like Forward Hold, Truck Pull, Dead Lift and loading very big objects.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S05 : E14 SCL 2018 Season 5, Episode 14, Road to Mexico
programme.desc: We bring you 50 minutes of Strongman inside. Fears, inspiration, courage, the best and worst from our finalists and their expectation of the finals. We also go to Poland and Germany to represent one day in the training of Krzysztof Radzikowski and Dennis Kohlruss. See all the finalists for Mexico in their comfort zone here, with their backgrounds /motivations /family and friends.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S05 : E15 SCL 2018 Season 5, Episode 15, Mexico - World Finals (Part 1)
programme.desc: The first part of the Strongman Champions League 2018 finals in Mexico. The last twelve athletes all pushing their boundaries and testing their limits to take the World title.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S05 : E16 SCL 2018 Season 5, Episode 16, Mexico - World Finals (Part 2)
programme.desc: After 11 months and 14 competitions all over the world, it all comes down to the final in this episode. The strongmen must show their best skills and every mistake is expensive, so their concentration must be at the highest possible level. Will Krzysztof manage to take off back or will Dainis maintain his lead?

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S06 : E01 SCL 2019 Season 6, Episode 1, World Strongest Viking
programme.desc: This year 14 athletes from all over the world came to Fefor to compete in 6 cruel events. Well see typical Viking disciplines on very heavy conditions in land of snow and ice, World records and athletes like the title defender Krzysztof Radzikowski, strongest guys from Holland and Germany and many more

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S06 : E02 SCL S6 Ep2 FIBO Power
programme.desc: The next stop in strongest league of the world is muscle capital, largest number of strong shoulders per capita in the World and of course, the most powerful host in Strongman champions league on the planet. It’s a FIBO - the biggest expo on planet Earth and the second stage of 2019 Strongman champions league, in Cologne, Germany.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S06 : E03 SCL 2019 Season 6, Episode 3, Turkey
programme.desc: On a spectacular beach in Alanya, the MLO Strongman Champions League Turkey was viewed by thousands of spectators over a two day battle. With 12 athletes at the start over 6 cruel events, like Marble Stone Lift, Truckpull and Deadlift cars. And with the comeback of Travis Ortmayer / USA, former stone king and world ranked competitor. Winner of several SCL stages in the past.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S06 : E04 SCL 2019 Season 6, Episode 4, Holland (Part 1)
programme.desc: Four times Strongest Man of Holland, Alex Moonen and the “Flying Dutchman” Kelvin de Ruiter competing here in Holland against 12 other strongest men in the world. There were 6 events in total, and 3 in this episode: The first event, a truckpull of 17.000 kg over 25 meters in max 75 seconds, was a real hard pull Also for the World Champion Truckpull, Holland’s runner-up Kelvin de Ruiter, but watch his amazing technique here.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S06 : E05 SCL 2019 Season 6, Episode 5, Holland (Part 2)
programme.desc: Strongest Man of Holland, Alex Moonen and the “Flying Dutchman” Kelvin de Ruiter, competing in Holland against 12 other strongest men in the world. There were 6 events in total, 3 in this second episode; a Viking-press of 150 kg with the current world record holder Luke Herrick. The fifth event, a front hold of 25 kg is loved or hated by the athletes and lastly, the Stones of Strength.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S06 : E06 SCL 2019 Season 6, Episode 6, Russia
programme.desc: An unbelievable TANK PULL of 50.000 kg was at the stage of SCL RUSSIA. Never seen this before! Not only a tank pull was done here but also the Viking Press/ Deadlift Max and Log lift reps were spectacular events to see here in Russia. With Mikhail Koklyaev also as event presenter, the former top 3 world strongest man from Russia was there

It is very important to them because they want to be able to have everyone comfortably visit and eventually retire here in a few years.

Currently, they live in a modest bungalow in a busy neighbourhood but would prefer to live in a secluded house with a magnificent view. Ideally, Giulia also wants a house that has separate living quarters for her ageing parents.

programme.sub-title: S03 : E03 Top Million Dollar Agent

Shannon has been accepted into the Ontario Veterinarian College at the University of Guelph, which is Canadas leading program in veterinary health care. This is the reason they are moving to Guelph. Kevin is happy to live anywhere as long as it has excellent golf courses. Eve will be glad to tell him that Guelph just happens to have 3 of the top ones in Ontario.

programme.sub-title: S03 : E04 Top Million Dollar Agent

Due to Marinos busy schedule as a producer, he would prefer a house that is all-inclusive and turnkey. Their kids are very active want a pool and the option for horse stables. Lauras going to find them the perfect home.

programme.title: Top Million Dollar Agent
programme.sub-title: S03 : E06 Top Million Dollar Agent
programme.desc: Diogo is a dedicated musician working on his new album. He has been debating between moving to Miami or staying in Canada. Toronto is closer to his family and where he feels at home with his music. Danielle will show him some spectacular properties in both cities and see what he decides.

programme.title: Top Million Dollar Agent
programme.sub-title: S03 : E07 Top Million Dollar Agent
programme.desc: Elizabeth and Michael are retired and want to move closer to their kids and grandchildren. They want to downsize from their two-story house into a bungalow. Luckily, Eve knows all about luxury bungalows. Elizabeth loves to exercise and really would like a gym. Michael has a passion for cars and needs at least a three-car garage. Their current house is dated so they would love a house that is turnkey. Eve will do her best to find their forever home.

programme.title: Top Million Dollar Agent
programme.sub-title: S03 : E08 Top Million Dollar Agent
programme.desc: Tomarra and Rob had just married and blended their two families. As a new family, they want to transition to a quiet neighbourhood away from the hustle and bustle of Toronto. Steve is up for the challenge. Rob is a writer and plans to work from home, while Tomarra is a naturopath who would love to have her own studio. Ultimately, they want to start cherishing the real things in life, and that is spending more time with their kids.

programme.title: Top Million Dollar Agent
programme.sub-title: S03 : E10 Top Million Dollar Agent
programme.desc: Kathryn and Neil are true urbanites. They love what downtown Toronto has to offer. When Neil found out his company was relocating to Guelph, they werent thrilled. After five months of long commutes, the Thompson family is ready to take the risk and make a move-with some conditions. The new house has to have a pool and playroom for the kids and a large entertainment area for adults. Eves challenge is to find them an enticing home that will convince their friends from the city to visit.

programme.title: Top Million Dollar Agent
programme.sub-title: S03 : E11 Top Million Dollar Agent
programme.desc: Ashley and Ali are ready to take their relationship and living situation to the next level. The young entrepreneurs are prepared to move into a house, but the one thing they cant agree on is where to live. Ashley wants an estate home outside the city that has an outdoor pool and beautifully manicured gardens. Ali, on the other hand, insists on being close to his downtown office and walking distance from restaurants and shops.

programme.title: Top Million Dollar Agent
programme.sub-title: S03 : E12 Top Million Dollar Agent
programme.desc: Stephanie is making a big move from BC to Guelph to be closer to her son John and his family. She doesnt want the move to be a hassle and is looking for an accessible, decent-sized home for her grandchildren and visitors from BC. Good sized guest rooms and a large backyard are a must. As she loves to cook, she would also like a new kitchen. Eve will show Stephanie 3 beautiful homes that fit the criteria. Stephanie is going to have a difficult decision.

programme.title: Top Million Dollar Agent
programme.sub-title: S03 : E13 Top Million Dollar Agent
programme.desc: Steve Bailey, Mike Donia and Daryl King review their favourite homes. Steve takes us down memory lane to his 18th century farmhouse, and another home with a stunning infinity pool. Daryls listings range from King city to Caloden, with helicopter pads and sprawling backyards. Mike brings us back to his fabulous listings in Thailand. He shows us a home made entirely of Bamboo, and billion-dollar property.

programme.title: Top Million Dollar Agent
programme.sub-title: S04 : E02 Top Million Dollar Agent
programme.desc: Suhail and Niki have busy schedules. Hes a marketing director and shes a doctor so shes often on call for a hospital downtown. Can they find a place that can help relieve stress, but also be close enough to downtown for those urgent calls? They want a secluded home with at least 1 acre and magnificent views.

programme.title: Top Million Dollar Agent
programme.sub-title: S04 : E03 Top Million Dollar Agent
programme.desc: Wendy and Daniel are looking to downsize after their kids have moved out, but still want an elegant home. Shes a physical therapist and shes a business analyst. They want something that can help them relax at the end of the day, with at least 4 bedrooms and away from the downtown core. Can Lou find them something that fits?

programme.title: Top Million Dollar Agent
programme.sub-title: S04 : E04 Top Million Dollar Agent
programme.desc: Danielle is helping quite a pair, Joseph is a chiropractor and Nadia is an aerospace engineer. Theyre looking for a home to start a family. Not only that, they want space to host their extended family. Will it be as difficult as rocket science?

programme.title: Top Million Dollar Agent
programme.sub-title: S04 : E05 Top Million Dollar Agent
programme.desc: Janelle and Manuel are young professionals looking for more space. With one child tagging along on the tour already, they need a place for their growing family. They might need to do some renovations, but they want everything to be perfect.

programme.title: Top Million Dollar Agent
programme.sub-title: S05 : E01 Top Million Dollar Agent
programme.desc: Vipins family of four are in the market to purchase their own dream home in the Greater Toronto Area.

programme.title: Top Million Dollar Agent
programme.sub-title: S05 : E02 Top Million Dollar Agent
programme.desc: Phil and Aubree, a newly wed couple, are in the market to purchase a dream home in Castlemore.

programme.title: Army of One
programme.desc: Ellen Hollman, som vi sett i Matrix 4, Spartacus och NCIS: New Orleans, i sitt livs roll som en nastintill ihjalslagen kvinna, vars hamnd ar skoningslos och grundlig. Ett ungt par åker ut for att talta i Alabamas skogar, men deras romantiska semester går fruktansvart fel nar de stoter på en våldsam drogkartell. Kartellens man dodar Brenners make Dillon (Matt Passmore) och lamnar Brenner att do – trodde de. Brenner, som mist allt, ger sig ut på en hamndaktion, som ingen kunnat vanta sig och som ingen undkommer. Filmen bjuder på en explosiv handling, som får tittaren att sitta som fastklistrad vid rutan, från borjan till slut!

programme.title: Flickan från tandsticksfabriken
programme.desc: Iris ar trott på sitt dodstråkiga jobb och liv. For att pigga upp stamningen beger hon sig ut på stan och shoppar en rod klanning. Natten spenderar hon med en rik man som lamnar henne en summa pengar morgonen efter. En tid senare upptacker Iris att hon ar gravid och upplyser den formogne mannen om sin situation, han skickar en ny bunt sedlar och ber henne att gora abort. Då går Iris ut och koper en stor mangd råttgift.

programme.title: Programmet fortsatter strax
programme.desc: Vi tar igen vår skonhetssomn! Stanna kvar for mer prisvard underhållning utvald av Rakuten TV.

programme.title: Tillbaka till Yorkshire
programme.desc: Arthur Morrison får reda på att han har cancer och att han bara har några veckor kvar att leva. Hans vuxna son Blake reser till Yorkshire for att bo hos sin mamma i byn dar han vaxte upp. Nar Arthurs tillstånd forvarras ser Blake tillbaka på sitt forhållande med pappan. Han minns saker de gjort tillsammans, fortroligheten mellan dem och aven de forbistringar de haft. Nar fadern dor borjar Morrison fundera kring det band de haft. Han ger tydligt uttryck for motsattningar, frustration, karlek och forlust som alla ar delar i det komplicerade forhållande som finns mellan en far och hans son.

programme.title: Southside With You
programme.desc: Sommaren 1989 i Chicago, och unge Barack Obama gor sig redo for att bjuda ut Michelle Robinson. Michelle å sin sida forsakrar sina foraldrar om att det inte ar någon dejt hon ska på. Men hur ska hon tillbringa en dag i hans sallskap, utan att falla for hans charm? Southside with You skildrar Barack och Michelle Obamas forsta dejt med oerhord noggrannhet från regissoren Richard Tanne. Filmen har kallats for historiens basta dejtfilm, och jamforts med Richard Linklaters Bara en natt och Bara en dag.

programme.title: What Maisie Knew
programme.desc: Maisie måste navigera i ett vuxen kaos med all sin oskuld, charm och villkorslosa karlek nar hon fastnar i mitten av foraldrarnas bittra vårdnadstvist. Den alltid observante Maisie kastas fram och tillbaka mellan sina foraldrar, Susanna, en åldrande rockstjarna, som jagar en sista ""hit"" och fadern Beale som ar en upptagen konsthandlare med många resdagar. Båda gifter sig med nya partners for att bli starkare i en vårdnadstvist samtidigt som Maisie knyter allt starkare band mellan sig o mammans nya pojkvan, bartendern Lincoln, inser hon att hon måste vara den vuxna i sin egen lilla familj.

programme.title: Cha Cha Cha
programme.desc: Den alkoholiserade Matti (Matti Pellonpaa), som bor under broarna, ar på vag att arva en betydande summa pengar från sin amerikanska faster. Men mannen måste vara representativ under fasterns besok. Matti berattar om situationen for sin van som arbetar som bilhandlare, och denne foreslår en rollbyten mot ersattning.

programme.title: 10 Years
programme.desc: Vem blev tjock? Vem blev rik? Vem blev snygg och vem har inte forandrats ett smack? Channing Tatum, Rosario Dawson och Chris Pratt återforenas på tidernas grymmaste återforeningsfest dar gamla roller axlas på nytt, karleksaffarer flammar upp igen och dar det helt enkelt INTE finns plats i garderoben for alla gamla skelett! 10 år har gått sedan de gick ut gymnasiet - men vissa saker forandrar sig aldrig!

programme.title: Moln på drift
programme.desc: Ilona och Lauri ar ett stravsamt par som inte begar mycket av livet. Tak over huvudet, mat på bordet, ett glas vin och en kvall framfor tv-n. De arbetar plikttroget och agnar sina korta ledigheter åt varandra och sin hund. Men en dag hander något som hotar att slå deras trygga tillvaro i spillror. En varm och absurd historia om ett alldeles vanligt par någonstans i Finland.

programme.title: What We Did On Our Holiday
programme.desc: Doug (David Tennant) och Abi (Rosamund Pike) ar två helt vanliga foraldrar med tre charmiga men valdigt excentriska barn. Nar det hårda foraldralivet hotar deras mentala halsa och aktenskap så bestammer de sig for att ta med barnen på en resa till Skottland till ett stort slaktkalas och for att halsa på Dougs minst sagt knappa pappa Gordie (Billy Connolly). Det som skulle bli en forsoningsresa forvandlas snabbt till ett hysteriskt roligt socialt katastrofområde nar osamja,

programme.title: Runaway Jury
programme.desc: Från mastaren John Grisham kommer en thriller med Dustin Hoffman, Gene Hackman, John Cusack och Rachel Weisz. En jury-fixare spelar ett dodligt katt-och-råtta-spel med en jurymedlem och en mystisk framling som båda erbjuder att "leverera" domen till hogstbjudande. Snart står både liv och miljoner på spel i en pulshojare full av ovantade vandningar.

programme.title: Happy Together
programme.desc: Ho och Lai reser till Argentina for att återfinna gnistan i sitt forhållande, men i stallet for en nytandning blåses den lilla lågan ut. Ingen av dem har råd med flygbiljetten hem, och har olika vagar att mota problemet på. Happy Together var Wong Kar-wais genombrott innan In the Mood For Love, och betraktas som en av de framsta HBTQ-filmerna från New Queer Cinema-rorelsen. Wong Kar-wai vann Basta regi for filmen vid filmfestivalen i Cannes.

programme.title: Barbarian
programme.desc: Nar hon anlander till Detroit for en anstallningsintervju hyr en ung kvinna ett hus. Men nar hon anlander sent på kvallen upptacker hon att huset ar dubbelbokat och att en frammande man redan bor dar. Fast hon vet battre, bestammer hon sig for att tillbringa kvallen i hemmet, men upptacker snart att det finns mer att frukta an en ovantad husgast.

programme.title: City By The Sea
programme.desc: "City by the Sea" ar den sanna berattelsen om NYPD-kriminalaren Vincent Lamara som ar på jakt efter annu en brutal mordare. Men i detta fall finns det bara en misstankt: Joey Lamara - hans egen son!

programme.title: Silent House
programme.desc: Insparrad i familjens avskilda stuga vid sjon, kampar en ung kvinna desperat for att bevara sitt forstånd, instangd i en skrackinjagande mardrom. Sarah forbereder, tillsammans med sin far och farbror, forsaljningen av familjens mångåriga stuga som nyligen harjats av inkraktare. Men trasiga fonster och sprickor i vaggarna visar sig vara det minsta av deras bekymmer nar de upptacker att de inte ar ensamma ... och att vaggarna doljer mer an bara mogel... "Silent House" ar baserad på en sann historia. Den ar filmad i ett långt, sammanhangande klipp ("real time") och overfor huvudpersonens kusligt realistiska kansla av stigande panik och skrack till betraktaren.

programme.title: County Line
programme.desc: Sheriffen och marinkårsveteranen Alden Rockwell forsoker anpassa sig till livet som civilperson efter att ha forlorat sheriffvalet, i alla fall tills hans gamle vapenbroder och sheriffen i granncountyt blir skjuten under mystiska omstandigheter. Alden blir genast pressad till att undersoka mordforsoket.

programme.title: Programmet fortsatter strax
programme.desc: Vi tar igen vår skonhetssomn! Stanna kvar for mer prisvard underhållning utvald av Rakuten TV.

programme.title: 10 Items or Less
programme.desc: Oscar och Golden Globevinnaren Morgan Freeman spelar har en filmstjarna som ger sig ut på rollforberedande research i ett snabbkop i ostra Los Angeles. Han moter en snabbtalande kassorska (Paz Vega) och de ger sig av på en gemensam resa for att visa varandra sina respektive varldar. Strandad utan vare sig mobiltelefon eller bil accepterar han tjejens erbjudande om att ge honom lift tillbaka till Beverly Hills. Under resans gång upptacker emellertid det har till synes omaka paret att de har vissa gemensamma namnare som for all framtid kommer att forandra deras syn på deras egna liv...

programme.title: Im Not There
programme.desc: Dylan gestaltas i denna film av vitt skilda skådespelare/skådesperskor i en serie av sammanvavda historier. "Im Not There" ar ett ovanligt och enastående portratt av Amerikas storste nu levande rockikon, Bob Dylan. Ovanligt eftersom hela sex skådespelare, unga som gamla, kvinnor som man och svarta som vita gestaltar Dylan. Enastående eftersom filmen ar den enda av många filmer om Dylan, som har fått legendens eget godtyckande och darmed den gyllene nyckeln till ett musikarkiv av narmast mytologisk karaktar. Resultatet ar en fenomenalt vacker hyllning till Bob Dylan och hans musik, och en fantastisk inblick i en musikalisk enstorings liv, som både fans och nyborjare kan gladjas over.

programme.title: My Week With Marilyn
programme.desc: I ett desperat forsok att bli tagen på storre allvar reser ikonen Marilyn Monroe (Michelle Williams) till London 1956 for att spela mot legenden Laurence Olivier i “Prinsen och balettflickan”. Den omhetstorstande Marilyn kanner sig overgiven av maken Arthur Miller och attraherad av Oliviers assistent, den unge Colin Clark. Colin blir snart Marilyns fasta och trygga punkt, samtidigt som han också blir Oliviers endahopp att kunna slutfora sin film genom sin formåga att hålla den impulsiva Marilyn i schakt. Upp over oronen foralskadar det nu Colins hjarta som riskerar att krossas av varldens storsta och vackraste filmstjarna!

programme.title: Instrument of War
programme.desc: Den amerikanska piloten Clair Cline blir nedskjuten och hamnar i fångenskap i norra Tyskland. En kamp tar slut, en annan tar vid – att hålla hoppet vid liv trots taggtråd och fortryck. Cline och hans medfångar måste hitta ett satt att hålla ihop, inte bara for att overleva utan aven for att utharda fångenskapen. Baserad på sanna handelser.

programme.title: The Fifth Estate
programme.desc: De borjade med att skapa en undergroundwebbplats och kom att bli varldens mest efterlysta personer. Men nar WikiLeaksgrundarnaJulian Assange och Daniel Domscheit-Berg kom over den storsta mangden sekretessbelagd underrattelseinformation som någonsin har lackt ut från det amerikanska forsvarsministeriet borjade en intern kamp. For vad ar priset for den fria varldens storsta hemligheter? Och vad kommer det att kosta att avsloja dem?

programme.title: Conviction
programme.desc: Nar Bettys bror falls for mord borjar en 18 år lång kamp mot systemet. Övertygad om broderns oskuld borjar Betty studera juridik så att hon sjalv kan forsvara sin bror i rattssalen!

programme.title: In Time
programme.desc: I en framtid dar tid ar bokstavligen pengar och åldrande stannar vid 25 år, ar det enda sattet att hålla sig vid liv att tjana, stjala eller arva mer tid. Kommer Salas att leva minut till minut, tills en tidsfall ger honom tillgång till den rika varlden, dar han lagar sig med en vacker ung arvtagare for att forstora det korrupta systemet.

programme.title: Birdman
programme.desc: I den omtalade och kritikerhyllade svarta komedin BIRDMAN eller The Unexpected Virtue of Ignorance ser vi Michael Keaton i huvudrollen som en skådespelare, mest kand for att ha spelat den ikoniska superhjalten Birdman. Han ska nu regissera en teateruppforestallning på Broadway och vi får folja honom under de hektiska dagarna innan den stora premiarkvallen. Samtidigt som han slåss mot sina inre demoner och sitt stora ego så forsoker han lappa ihop både familj och karriar. For regi står Alejandro G. Iñárritu (BABEL, ÄLSKADE HUNDAR) och i ovriga roller ser vi bl.a. Zach Galifianakis, Edward Norton, Emma Stone, Naomi Watts.

programme.title: Det låsta rummet
programme.desc: Sean och Derek ar två småtjuvar specialiserade på att ta anstallning på restaurangparkeringar, med syfte att lansa rika gasters hem medan de ar borta. Under inbrottet hos den formogne Cale Erendreich finner Sean en hemlig dorr som han dyrkar upp.

programme.title: Spring Breakers
programme.desc: Brit, Candy, Cotty och Faith drommer om att åka på Spring Break, amerikanska collegeungdomars årliga festvecka, men har inte råd. De bestammer sig for att råna en restaurang for att finansiera sin resa och snart ar de på vag till Florida for att parta loss. Men knappt hinner festen borja forran de arresteras och hamnar i fangelse. Till deras raddning kommer knarklangaren och smågangstern Alien som betalar deras borgen och tar dem med på ett Spring Break-aventyr de sent ska glomma.

programme.title: Flickan från tandsticksfabriken
programme.desc: Iris ar trott på sitt dodstråkiga jobb och liv. For att pigga upp stamningen beger hon sig ut på stan och shoppar en rod klanning. Natten spenderar hon med en rik man som lamnar henne en summa pengar morgonen efter. En tid senare upptacker Iris att hon ar gravid och upplyser den formogne mannen om sin situation, han skickar en ny bunt sedlar och ber henne att gora abort. Då går Iris ut och koper en stor mangd råttgift.

programme.title: Arlington Road
programme.desc: I denna tata thriller moter vi collegeprofessorn Michael Faraday vars fru, en FBI-agent, dodats av medlemmar av en hogerextrem terroristgrupp. Nar Michael blir van med sina nya grannar, Oliver och Cheryl Lang, får han snart anledning att misstanka att något inte står ratt till. Han borjar forska i deras forflutna, men inte utan risk for sitt liv.

programme.title: Boarding Pass

programme.desc: Emeline goes to Ruka-Kuusamo, where she tries river rafting. She also meets a reindeer herder,who tells her about the unique ways of herding reindeer.

programme.title: Xplore Bhutan
programme.desc: Actress and travel enthusiast, Radhika Bangia explores the enigma that is Bhutan, when she visits Thimpu, the capital city with no traffic lights and no skyscrapers invading the skyline. Here, she checks out significant sights such as the Tibetan-style National Memorial Chorten, the National Library and the Folk Heritage Museum in order to understand more about the beliefs, history, architecture and cuisine of Bhutan.

programme.title: World Heritage

programme.title: Xplore Bhutan
programme.desc: Known as Druk Yul or the “Land of the Thunder Dragon”, Bhutan is the country of mountains, monasteries and mystery. Radhika Bangia finds this to be true when she visits Punakha, the former capital of Bhutan, where she marvels at the architecture of Punakha Dzong and gets to know the story behind the two rivers, Mo Chhu and Po Chhu. She also explores the sacred temples and Mebar Tsho lake of Bumthang, the religious heart of Bhutan, and gets to know the local legends.

programme.title: World Spas

programme.title: 10 Days Scotland
programme.desc: Robbie’s journey to reconnect with his Scottish roots begins in Edinburgh, the stunning capital city perched on extinct volcanoes. Navigating the twists of the Royal Mile, strutting around the majestic Edinburgh castle and learning to sip scotch like a true Scotsman, he feels a tad closer to his heritage. The real fun kicks in, however, when he stumbles onto a rather flamboyant way to unleash his inner Highlander.

programme.title: Xplore Bulgaria
programme.desc: Like Rome, Plovdiv straddles seven hills; but as Europe’s oldest continuously inhabited city, it’s far more ancient. As Catriona takes a tour of the city to see its iconic attractions such as a Roman Amphitheatre, which was once the setting for gladiator fights, and the striking Baroque Saints Constantine and Helena Church, she begins to see how seamlessly modern life blends with the age-old ruins. Along the way, she realizes why Plovdiv is called the ‘Eternal City’ of Bulgaria.

programme.desc: Like Rome, Plovdiv straddles seven hills; but as Europe’s oldest continuously inhabited city, it’s far more ancient. Along the way, she realizes why Plovdiv is called the ‘Eternal City’ of Bulgaria.

programme.desc: A former school teacher reinvents herself when she discovers a passion for sharing other women’s stories. Thanks to a successful crowdfunding campaign, this dream blossomed into a professional career in journalism and she launched a print mook (magazine and book) called Etonnantes. Etonnantes features interviews of women of all backgrounds, celebrating their diversity and success in each field.

programme.desc: The call of the Forest is about discovering places but above all it is about meeting those who protect this priceless heritage. Forests are essential to mankind. With nearly 1,000 varieties (soft cheeses, cooked, blue-veined, pressed cheeses…), the French are the biggest consumers of cheese in the world!

programme.title: Carine (Nice)
programme.sub-title: S01 : E01 My Zen People - Season 4 - Carine (Nice)
programme.desc: After twenty years as a lawyer, Carine decided to give in to her desire to help others heal. Her inner journey led her to discover a passion for naturopathy as she rediscovered her love for nature and learned the healing qualities of the plants around her. Combined with a deep understanding of astrology and nutrition, she is now able to help others live better and find their own path.

programme.title: Virginie (Lyon)
programme.sub-title: S01 : E01 My Zen People - Season 4 - Virginie (Lyon)
programme.desc: Virginie’s beautiful handwritten lettering decorates the walls and windows of many shops in and around Lyon, France, as she lives out her passion of finding beauty in every stroke. A former waitress, Virginie was struggling to find her calling when she suffered a life-altering horse accident that almost left her handicapped. At only 30, she was forced to put her whole life into perspective. She finally found herself through a love for graphic design and lettering, combined with a desire for freedom that came with working independently. To motivate other women, she has also launched “Ladyboss”, a network of inspiring women entrepreneurs.

programme.title: Laetitia (French Alps)
programme.sub-title: S01 : E01 My Zen People - Season 4 - Laetitia (French Alps)
programme.desc: While pregnant with her daughter, Laetitia, a former journalist, experienced a strong desire to change lifestyles and move to the countryside. Remembering the teachings of her grandmother, she began to venture outdoors into the surrounding Alps and study the different plants at her fingertips. Today she holds a wealth of knowledge about the medicinal and aromatherapeutic value of plants that she applies to making natural products. With utmost respect for the environment, Laetitia gathers only what she needs in order to make herbal infusions.

programme.title: Louise (Oleron Island)
programme.sub-title: S01 : E01 My Zen People - Season 4 - Louise (Oleron Island)
programme.desc: At only 20 years old, Louise is full of confidence and already achieved a personal dream of hers to share her passion for nutritious and locally-sourced ingredients on the island of Oleron, France. Repurposing a camping car, she set up a brunch and tea-time spot where the guests can hand-pick their ingredients in the adjacent organic fields. Louise transforms the ingredients into favourite creations of hers and even joins her father for boat trips when she needs to stock up on fresh fish for the menu!

programme.title: Japan: Mass consumption - What the labels forget to mention - Part 1
programme.sub-title: S01 : E01 Earth from above - Season 3 - Japan: Mass consumption - What the labels forget to mention - Part 1
programme.desc: In this instalment, Yann Arthus-Bertrand lifts the veil on the products people buy. Almost everything we buy has a direct impact on our environment. We head to Japan to talk about the impact of new technologies, then to the Republic of Congo in Bukavu for the coltan harvest. How does our total consumption affect the environment? What permanent brands are we imposing on our planet? How can we differentiate between useful and useless purchases?

programme.sub-title: S01 : E01 Earth from above - Season 3 - Japan: Mass consumption - What the labels forget to mention - Part 2
programme.desc: Above all, these reports are an opportunity for Yann Arthus-Bertrand to take stock of the planet and denounce certain human behaviors that are at the root of dramatic, even irreversible, environmental and climatic degradation. Off to Tokyo, then Kenya, to an animal sanctuary. Then on to Mount Fuji to learn how to live there, and all the plastic that clogs up the seas. Reports will focus on everyday products, chosen for their destructive production practices for both people and the environment.

programme.title: The taste of bread
programme.sub-title: S01 : E01 Julies Frenchy Cookbook - Season 4 - The taste of bread
programme.desc: Today, Julie takes you on a bread trail to uncover the dedicated artisan bakers and millers. Her adventure will lead her through the Libourne region, then onwards to the North of France, the Ardèche, and the Aisne, where bakers have transformed bread into a powerful catalyst for social cohesion. While some individuals may avoid bread, particularly due to gluten-related concerns, others have chosen to reposition it at the forefront of the dining experience by championing its nutritional benefits. This commitment is shared by several chefs whom Julie will meet at the conclusion of her expedition.

programme.title: Juliette (Morbihan)
programme.sub-title: S01 : E01 My Zen People - Season 4 - Juliette (Morbihan)
programme.desc: Juliette has long been aware of the delicate beauty of nature. For years she spent her life on the sea, organising regattas for the traditional sailboats that are famous in the French region of Morbihan. Her appreciation for the elements made for a smooth transition as she decided to leave the water behind and return to the earth. Learning to shape a ball of clay into a graceful and elegant object, she discovered a passion for ceramics. Today, she lives from her creations and makes pieces that reflect their surroundings, the stunning Gulf of Morbihan.

programme.title: Anna (Brittany)
programme.sub-title: S01 : E01 My Zen People - Season 4 - Anna (Brittany)
programme.desc: Anna’s unusual background provided inspiration for her life change. Her career began as a wolf trainer for cinema and it was during these years that she developed her deep love for animals. After being tired of seeing them used as props and constantly in cages, she decided to leave the world of show business behind and start an eco-friendly sheep and goat pasture. To further share her passion for these gentle animals, Anna has opened a conservatory farm where visitors can experience first-hand the joys of being close to nature. She also makes amazing goat cheese!

programme.title: Cristina (Spain)
programme.sub-title: S01 : E01 My Zen People - Season 4 - Cristina (Spain)
programme.desc: At 31 years old, the last thing Cristina expected when she went to see the doctor about a blocked ear was to leave the consultation with a diagnosis for Breast Cancer. This young and passionate sociologist decided to apply the same philosophy to her treatment as she did when surfing: when a wave crashes down on you, get up and try again. Through her healing journey she deepened her love for the ocean and also discovered the therapeutic capabilities of yoga for cancer patients. Today she shares her practice through surf and yoga retreats and is specialised in oncological yoga, helping others heal.

programme.title: Idoia (Spain)
programme.sub-title: S01 : E01 My Zen People - Season 4 - Idoia (Spain)
programme.desc: Idoia thrives on weaving together the sources of inspiration that surround her. Heavily influenced by the natural beauty of her home region of Galicia, Spain, she creates unique woven pieces from diverse and beautiful materials. Idoia’s pieces represent her vision of a modern woman, drawing from the traditions and experiences of those who perfected the craft before her and also pushing to innovate and adapt her creations for the modern world. Her recent collaboration with luxury fashion house Loewe is a dream come true for this modern artisan.

programme.title: Nature’s Heroes: Bangladesh - Part 1
programme.sub-title: S01 : E01 Earth from above - Season 4 - Nature’s Heroes: Bangladesh - Part 1
programme.desc: With Bangladesh as a running thread, Yann Arthus-Bertrand meets several people who have changed their lives to dedicate themselves to a major project. In Bangladesh, Yves and Runa Marre have created the Friendship Foundation. Among other things, they’ve created a floating hospital installed on an old barge bought in France. Julie Andersen, an ex-advertising executive from New York has come to South Africa to defend sharks with her Shark Angels Foundation. In North India, Kartik Satyanarayan is helping to stop the dreadful exploitation of the lippus bears (dancing bears). He’s created Wildlife SOS, a preserve to rehabilitate the bears that have been rescued and to give work to the men of...

programme.desc: The Qatar Airways GKA Kite World Tour 2024 will host the second stop of the freestyle discipline in Cauipe in north-eastern Brazil. The Copa Kitley GKA Freestyle Kite World Cup offers intense competitions in the shallow waters.

programme.title: GWA Wingfoil World Cup 2024 – Ibiraquera (BRA) – Overall Highlights
programme.desc: Ibiraquera is the venue for the GWA Wingfoil World Cup 2024, where the worlds best wingfoilers will meet. With its constant winds and breathtaking coastline, this Brazilian hotspot provides the perfect backdrop for exciting races.

programme.title: GKA Kite-Surf World Cup 2024 – Ibiraquera (BRA) – Overall Highlights
programme.desc: Ibiraquera is the venue for the GKA Kite-Surf World Cup 2024, which brings together the best kitesurfers in the world. Athletes from all over the world will compete for the title and show impressive skills in surfing and strapless freestyle.

programme.title: Fond of Font
programme.desc: Seb Berthe and Hugo Parmentier have set themselves quite a challenge: to complete 100 7A boulders on a single day. An extraordinary journey of over 80 km, when you consider how demanding these rocks are. Crimps, falls, slips but above all a magnificent human adventure.

programme.title: Emocean - Surf Documentary
programme.desc: Today we take you on an unparalleled surf trip to some of the most famous, as well most terrifying waves on the planet. We will listen to some intimate stories of extraordinary people literally living IN and WITH the ocean.

programme.title: Tenerife Blue Trail
programme.desc: We are back in Tenerife, one of the highlights of the ultra running calendar, for the 10th edition of the Tenerife Blue Trail. Tenerife is described as an outdoor gym open 365 days a year - a paradise for every athlete.

programme.title: FIA Karting Grand Prix - European Karting Championship
programme.desc: Karting is a great life school for young people. The FIA ​​Karting Championships are open to drivers aged 12 and over and there is no upper age limit.

programme.title: The Barrel - Part I
programme.desc: "The Barrel" is a cinematic tribute to moments in big waves. This program takes a journey to some legendary barrel destinations - Hawaiis Pipeline, Indonesia and Kirra on Australias Gold Coast.

programme.title: The Barrel - Part II
programme.desc: The Barrel is a cinematic tribute to those big-wave moments. This program takes a journey to some legendary barrel destinations - Hawaiis Pipeline, Indonesia and Kirra on Australias Gold Coast.

programme.title: The history of competitive Snowboarding
programme.desc: This Competition is in human nature. But that was far from the thoughts of early pioneers in the nineteen hundreds or those of Mister Sherman Poppin of Michigan. In the Christmas of 1965 he invented the Snurfer. This changed the history of snowsports.

programme.title: Eternal Flame
programme.desc: To jump from the top of Nameless Tower in Pakistan (6200m) after climbing the Eternal Flame route is to combine the ascent of one of the most beautiful climbing routes in the world with the opening of one of the most breathtaking BASE jumping exits imaginable.

programme.title: Catch the Moment - Profile Robbie Maddison
programme.desc: Robbie Maddison began his career competing in national motocross competitions. On New Years Eve 2007, the 40th anniversary of Evel Knievels legendary jump over the Caesars Palace fountain, the Australian broke the world record in the bicycle long jump with his bicycle

programme.title: 4Islands - Croatia
programme.desc: 4Islands MTB Croatia will welcome over 370 mountain bikers from all over the world for a five-day race on four Croatian islands. This year the order of the islands will be slightly different, starting with Krk, Cres, Lošinj and ending on Rab.

programme.title: World E-Bike Series Round #1 and #2
programme.desc: Welcome from WES Round 1 and 2 in Trentino, Alto Garda, for the UCI E-MTB XC World Cup Season Opener. First time ever in the astonishing Dolomites mountain area in northern Italy, well-known for its tradition in e-biking, MTB and cyclo-tourism.

programme.title: Ötztal Cycle Marathon (AUT)
programme.desc: The Ötztal Cycle Marathon 2024 in Austria, taking place on the 1st of September, is the most challenging cycling marathon in the Alps, offering a captivating mix of valley and high alpine terrain. The course spans 227 kilometers and over 4,000 participants.

programme.title: Titan Desert Series 2024 - Almeria (ESP)
programme.desc: The rugged landscapes of Almería, Spain, hosts one of the most challenging mountain bike races in the world - the Škoda Titan Desert Series. Over rocky trails and under the scorching Spanish sun, elite riders push their limits in this multi-stage endurance race.

programme.title: Mammut Biggest Peak Project 3 - Cerro Kishtwar
programme.desc: Mammut 150 Peaks Project: Cerro KishtwarKashmir, India, holds some of the world’s most spectacular and mystical mountains. Now with special permissions, an European team will attempt to climb the most aesthetic one of all, Cerro Kishtwar.

programme.title: Mammut Biggest Peak Project 4 - Italy and Norway
programme.desc: 150 summit projectTwo speed flyers were the first to climb Mount Etna (ITA) with paragliders and skis. Another exciting ski tour was undertaken by Scandinavian sportswomen who climbed Geitgaljen in the Lofoten Islands (NOR) in April 2012.

programme.title: Mammut Biggest Peak Project 5 - Patagonia,Alaska and Pakistan
programme.desc: Stephan Siegrist climbs all the summits of the Cerro Torre group in Patagonia / The Ataraxia Mammut Proteam wanted to climb Mt. Marcus Baker with kitesupport in Alaska / David Lama intends to climb the 6,251 meter peak of Trango Tower in Pakistan

programme.title: FIA Karting Grand Prix - European Karting Championship

programme.title: FIA – Intercontinental Drifting Cup 2021
programme.desc: In todays Episode we´re pulling the handbreak tight and put the pedal to the medal with the best professional drift driver. The Intercontinental Drifting Cup took place in Riga, Lativa this year. Cars up to 850 horse powers and a challenging track!

programme.title: Red Bull Romaniacs
programme.desc: The Red Bull Romaniacs Extreme Enduro Rally is open! From today until Saturday, the best hard enduro riders will take on the toughest rally in the world in Romania! The Red Bull Romaniacs takes place every year and attracts participants from around 50 countries.

programme.title: Simple Session 2024 - BMX Final
programme.desc: Simple Session was born in 2000, starting as a small-town competition, it has now blossomed into one of the worlds largest and most prestigious BMX and skateboarding contests. Simple Session 24 is set on August 24-25, promising a spectacular festival!

programme.title: Reconnect One - USA
programme.desc: Sarka and Cheryl, who havent seen each other in years, have decided to reunite and embark on a tour of their own. Having once traveled together on the contest scene for over 15 years, life led them to different corners of the West Coast of America.

programme.title: Swissway to Heaven
programme.desc: Swissway to Heaven is a film about multi-pitch climbing in the swiss alps.The dokumentary portraits the history and evolution of climbing in Swizerland aswell as Cedric Lachats adventure climbing all 5 big walls of the swiss alps.

programme.title: GKA World Tour Season Wrap Up
programme.desc: The Qatar Airways GKA Kite World Tour has just wrapped up a record-breaking year packed with drama and excitement. The stars of the sport pushed kiteboarding to new highs in 2023 in their single-minded quest for world titles.
